article.description: — Keith Higgins Jr. scored 19 points as Lehigh beat Cairn 88-33 on Saturday.
article.headline: Higgins scores 19 as Lehigh defeats Cairn 88-33
article.linkText: Higgins scores 19 as Lehigh defeats Cairn 88-33
article.story: BETHLEHEM, Pa. -- — Keith Higgins Jr. scored 19 points as Lehigh beat Cairn 88-33 on Saturday. Higgins was 8 of 10 shooting (3 for 5 from 3-point range) for the Mountain Hawks (2-7). Tyler Whitney-Sidney added 15 points while shooting 6 for 7, including 2 for 3 from beyond the arc, and they also had six rebounds. Joshua Ingram had 14 points and was 6 of 9 shooting (2 for 4 from 3-point range). Owen Bradford led the way for the Highlanders with six points. Christian Rivera added six points for Cairn. In addition, Josh Forker finished with five points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
